# E-Commerce Web Application

## Overview
This is a fully functional e-commerce web application built with Python/Django (or your framework). It includes all standard e-commerce features and supports online payment integration. The application allows users to browse products, manage carts, and complete purchases, while admins can manage products and categories.

---

## Features

### **User Features**
- Browse products by category
- View product details
- Add products to cart
- Update or remove items in the cart
- Checkout and make payments (payment gateway integrated)
- Order history (optional)
- Responsive UI

### **Admin Features**
- Add, update, and delete product categories
- Add, update, and delete products
- View orders and manage inventory
- Dashboard with product statistics (optional)

---

## Technology Stack
- **Backend:** Python, Django (or your backend framework)
- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap
- **Database:** SQLite / MySQL (as configured)
- **Payment Gateway:** Razorpay / Stripe / PayPal (test mode enabled)
- **Version Control:** Git & GitHub

